isApprovedOrOwner.t.sol
├── when the stream does not exist
│  └── it should return false
└── when the stream exists
   ├── when the caller is neither the owner nor approved
   │  └── it should return false
   ├── when the caller is the owner
   │  └── it should return true
   ├── when the caller is the approved for only one stream
   │  └── it should return true
   └── when the caller is the approved for all the streams
      └── it should return true
